    <section>

        <h1 data-ref="title">
            Title<br><small><dfn>1f2625c2-615f-11e3-bf13-d231feb1dc81</dfn></small>
        </h1>

        <p>The attribute <var>1f2625c2-615f-11e3-bf13-d231feb1dc81</var> is a string that defines the title of an application.</p>

        <pre data-attribute-schema="1f2625c2-615f-11e3-bf13-d231feb1dc81"></pre>

    </section>

    <section>

        <h1 data-ref="description">
            Description<br><small><dfn>b7856963-4078-4698-8e95-8feceafe78da</dfn></small>
        </h1>

        <p>The attribute <var>b7856963-4078-4698-8e95-8feceafe78da</var> is a string that provides a description for an application.</p>

        <p>This string may include basic HTML entities, such as <var>p</var>, <var>li</var>, <var>ul</var>, <var>ol</var> and <var>h1-6</var>. User-agents should respect these tags. They may respect additional tags. User-agents should not assume that this string contains only safe tags though, and sanitization is recommended.</p>

        <p>If no HTML tags are used, then user agents should assume that the text is formatted with whitespace. In such cases, user agents should replace newlines with <var>br</var> and/or <var>p</var> tags.</p>

        <pre data-attribute-schema="b7856963-4078-4698-8e95-8feceafe78da"></pre>

    </section>

    <section>

        <h1 data-ref="short_description">
            Short Description<br><small><dfn>c4ed1e3c-9ed7-4355-b293-3ed2fbb4a5fb</dfn></small>
        </h1>

        <p>The attribute <var>c4ed1e3c-9ed7-4355-b293-3ed2fbb4a5fb</var> is a string that provides a short description for an application. This should not exceed 80 characters, and engines may trim it if it does.</p>

        <pre data-attribute-schema="c4ed1e3c-9ed7-4355-b293-3ed2fbb4a5fb"></pre>

    </section>

    <section>

        <h1 data-ref="categories">
            Categories<br><small><dfn>c80df319-d5da-4f59-8ca3-c89b234c5055</dfn></small>
        </h1>

        <p>The attribute <var>c80df319-d5da-4f59-8ca3-c89b234c5055</var> is an array of strings that define categories for an application.</p>

        <pre data-attribute-schema="c80df319-d5da-4f59-8ca3-c89b234c5055"></pre>

    </section>

    <section>

        <h1 data-ref="tags">
            Tags<br><small><dfn>c6e33506-b170-475b-83e9-4ecd6b6dd42a</dfn></small>
        </h1>

        <p>The attribute <var>c6e33506-b170-475b-83e9-4ecd6b6dd42a</var> is an array of strings that define tags for an application.</p>

        <pre data-attribute-schema="c6e33506-b170-475b-83e9-4ecd6b6dd42a"></pre>

    </section>

    <section>

        <h1 data-ref="authors">
            Authors<br><small><dfn>d59e3a1f-c034-4309-a282-60228089194e</dfn></small>
        </h1>

        <p>The attribute <var>d59e3a1f-c034-4309-a282-60228089194e</var> is an object or an array of objects that provide name and contact details for one or more authors of an application.</p>

        <pre data-attribute-schema="d59e3a1f-c034-4309-a282-60228089194e"></pre>

    </section>

    <section>

        <h1 data-ref="organization">
            Organization<br><small><dfn>273c148d-de83-499e-b554-4cac9b262ab6</dfn></small>
        </h1>

        <p>The attribute <var>273c148d-de83-499e-b554-4cac9b262ab6</var> is an object that provides the name and basic information about the authoring organization for an application.</p>

        <pre data-attribute-schema="273c148d-de83-499e-b554-4cac9b262ab6"></pre>

    </section>

    <section>

